elements.name: totalAntidumpingDuty
elements.description: A value representing the total antidumping duty. Two decimal places are implied. If the duty is a whole number, the two low-order (cents) positions contain zeroes.

elements.name: totalCountervailingDuty
elements.description: A value representing the total countervailing duty amount. Two decimal places are implied. If the duty is a whole number, the two low-order (cents) positions contain zeroes.

elements.name: totalAmountDue
elements.description: A value representing the total amount due. Two decimal places are implied. If the amount is a whole number, the two low-order (cents) positions contain zeroes.

elements.name: totalInterestAmountForReconciliationSummary
elements.originalName: Total Interest Amount For Reconciliation Summary
elements.description: A value representing the total interest amount for reconciliation summary. Two decimal places are implied. If the interest is a whole number, the two low-order (cents) positions contain zeroes.

elements.name: totalNumberRevenueProducingEntries
elements.description: The number of total revenue-producing entries in the transaction.

elements.name: totalNumberNonRevenueProducingEntries
elements.description: The total number of non-revenue producing entries in the transaction.
